  sprite_front: {fileID: -3250029994485753652, guid: 8b62a6785a4f6664da5e47b832b3df3f, type: 3}
  infoCursor: Rest spot
  infoDescription: "Stopped at a scenic viewpoint, \nasked someone nearby \nto take
    a photo\nthe picture turned out blurry tho."
  descriptionVariants:
  - "Stopped at a scenic viewpoint, \nasked someone nearby to take a photo the picture
    turned out blurry tho."
  - "Hiked 2 km to see a waterfall \u2014 \nit was completely dry."
  - "Scenic viewpoint is under renovation, \nbut still stopped just to see the fence
    anyway."
  - "Visited a temple because the sign said,\n\u201CMonk gives accurate lottery numbers.\u201D"
  - "Stopped at a souvenir market, \nbought some durians \u2014\nand now the whole
    car smells."
  - "Visited a sheep farm \u2014 \nall the sheep were hiding from the sun, \nso we
    only get to see the birds..."
  - "Found a cute roadside caf\xE9,\nwent in alone, \ncame out with a car-full of
    souvenirs."
  - "Entered a national park, \ndrove really far in \u2014 \nended up with no signal
    \ntook us a while to get out."
  - "Checked in at a famous social media spot \u2014 \nturned out it was the size
    of a milk carton."
  - "Went to see the sea of mist, \narrived at noon \u2014 \nthere was only the sun..."
  isGoal: 0
  isImpassable: 0
